    BackgroundTaskUtil.Callback<R>

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    BackgroundTaskUtil
    Static class that allows background work to be done, then consume the result using BackgroundTaskUtil.Callback when the task has been finished.

    Utility class used to perform operations involving WeatherLocation

    Miscellaneous methods used through out the app
    NotificationUtil
    Class containing variables used in processing notifications
    WeatherJsonUtil
    Utility class used to parse host server Weather JSONObject(s) into: WeatherToday object WeatherObject object WeatherDay object WeatherHour object AstroElement object

    Class that holds all methods and formats to derive Date and Time strings
